      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STILTON QUINN (3) had the drop on the lead early on but could only manage second, beaten 2.75 lengths (23.30) at this track in a Maiden over 401m. Capable of going well again. TOM TRICKERY (2) finished well back on debut (23.71) at this track then better for the experience broke through last time to score a 2.75 lengths maiden win (22.83) at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. One of the leading chances again. DASHING DARLENE (8) jumped from the squeeze on debut and ran an eye catching race, finishing second at this track over 401m (23.03). Expected to do much better this time. BAUXITE LASS (1) placed last time and is worth some thought.",
